            View Facilities
          </Text>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-row max-md:flex-col w-full gap-20 justify-between">
        <div class="max-md:order-2">
          <Text type="h3">
            <span class="text-primary">STEM</span> Labs
          </Text>
          <div class="p-2"></div>
          <Text type="base" class="w-[90%]">
            Explore our modern STEM labs at Ekam, where curiosity meets
            innovation. They are meticulously designed, adhering to the highest
            safety standards. Here, students embark on hands-on experiments,
            unlocking the mysteries of science and technology in an environment
            that sparks intellectual curiosity and creativity.
          </Text>
          <div class="p-3"></div>
          <Text
            type="sm"
            class="uppercase text-primary underline tracking-widest font-semibold cursor-pointer"
            data-modal-target="science-labs"
            data-target-deck="deck-science-labs"
          >
            View Labs
          </Text>
        </div>
        <DeckCard
          class="relative"
          images={[
            { src: campus6.src, alt: "campus1" },
            { src: campus7.src, alt: "campus2" },
            // {src: slide3, alt: 'campus3'},
          ]}
          target="science-labs"
          id="deck-science-labs"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-row max-md:flex-col w-full gap-20 justify-between">
        <DeckCard
          class="relative left-2 max-md:-left-2"
          images={[
            { src: campus9.src, alt: "campus1" },
            { src: campus10.src, alt: "campus2" },
            // {src: slide3, alt: 'campus3'},
          ]}
          target="sports-facilities"
          id="deck-sports-facilities"
        />
        <div>
          <Text type="h3">
            <span class="text-primary">Sports</span> Facilities
          </Text>
          <div class="p-2"></div>
          <Text type="base" class="w-[90%]">
            Sports ensure the good physical, mental and emotional health of children.
            Ekam International has outstanding infrastructure with vibrant sports facilities. 
            <br/><br/>
            School has two magnificent grounds for football, kabaddi, kho kho and athletics, well structured basketball and volleyball courts, well equipped & well netted cricket arena, well fenced skating arena with smooth flooring. Indoor games like chess, carom, TT etc along with one well designed & structured swimming pool.

            <!-- International size courts and sports infrastructure as well as
            expert professional coaches support a variety of sport activities
            like swimming, basketball, football, volleyball, chess, handball,
            netball, karate, cricket, skating, lawn tennis, and
            badminton.
            <br />
            <br />
             The students are also exposed to opportunities to participate in
            varied recreational programs that include gymnastics, aerobics,
            yoga, athletics and exercise. -->
          </Text>
          <div class="p-3"></div>
          <Text
            type="sm"
            class="uppercase text-primary underline tracking-widest font-semibold cursor-pointer"
            data-modal-target="sports-facilities"
            data-target-deck="deck-sports-facilities"
          >
            View Sport Facilities
          </Text>
        </div>
