        Ekam International has 20 buses well equipped with GPS & CCTV. Ekam school buses are spacious with a required capacity to accommodate students. Every bus has a teacher and helper to ensure proper discipline & safety of students. School bus drivers are responsible to pick & drop the children to their respective stops.
      </Text>
      <div class="p-3"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-row items-center">
        <div class="w-[14px] h-[17px]">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="100%"
            height="100%"
            viewBox="0 0 14 17"
            fill="none"
          >
            <path d="M14 8.5L0.499999 16.7272L0.5 0.272758L14 8.5Z" fill="white"
            ></path>
